(2, 1, 5, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, 'finance-and-operations', 'none', 'know-your-costs-stock-photo-18628914-piggy-bank-with-savings-message-1200.jpg', 'none', 'Know your costs', 'none', 'Harry Colbert, Jr.', 'none', 'Oprah Winfrey famously said she personally signs every check that hermulti-billion dollar empire issues.', 'none', 'Oprah Winfrey famously said she personally signs every check that her multi-billion dollar empire issues. She made the statement when talking to a recording star that had made millions of dollars, yet was forced to file for bankruptcy. But that couldnt happen to you, right? Or could it? This is not to be meant as a scare tactic, but a serious wakeup call. Are you on top of your business finances? Even when your operation is small, finances can get away from you. And the more you grow, the harder it is to track your spending. The bottom line is the bottom line!<i>Tips to control spending</i>The first thing any business owner should do is to have (and staywithin) a monthly budget. Remember to account for<i>all</i>of your monthly expenses. This includes your lease, utilities, any equipment costs, maintenance costs (if applicable), payroll, etc. Oh, and dont forget your taxes! The static costs (lease, phone, Internet, etc.) are easy to calculate, but youll have to estimate your fluctuating costs. I always try to overestimate these costs, just to be on the safe side.<i>Sweat the small stuff</i>Everything costs! Theres nothing wrong with being accused of being a penny-pincher or a tightwad. Im not saying become obsessive about things, but avoid paying extra for some of your daily use items. Items such as ink and toner can become an absolute drain on resources. Any time you can buy in bulk and reduce your unit costs, do so. Search for the most competitive phone and Internet packages  and examine your bill. Oftentimes companies will sign you up at one rate, only for that rate to balloon months later. A lot of this advice may seem elementary, but when in the heat of day-to-day operations, and focusing on ones profession (being a lawyer, doctor, architect, contractor, etc.), oftentimes business owners forget to focus on the business. But remember, your profession doesnt make the money the business does. ', 'br', 1368719580, '', 'none', 'Know your costs', 'none', 'Know your costs - Oprah Winfrey famously said she personally signs every check that her multi-billion dollar empire issues.', 'none', 'costs, oprah, spending,small stuff, knowledge', 'none', 'Know your costs', 'none', 'stock-photo-1579457-balancing-checkbook.jpg', 'none', 'Know your costs - Oprah Winfrey famously said she personally signs every check that her multi-billion dollar empire issues.', 'none', 'Editor Insight News; Entrepreneur; CEO Thee Urbane Life', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', 'Know your costs', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', 0, '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', 0, 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', 'know-your-costs-stock-photo-18628914-piggy-bank-with-savings-message-360.jpg', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none'),
