(5, 1, 5, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, 'leadership-and-growth', 'none', 'LISA-PRICE-SCREEN-SAVER.jpg', 'none', 'Feel the Fear and Do It Anyway!', 'none', 'Alshante Squire', 'none', 'Starting a business can be frightening task. There''s always times in your business when you''re afraid" says Lisa.', 'none', 'Starting a business can be a frightening task for anyone to take on.<i>There are always times in your business when you are afraid</i>says Lisa Price Founder of Carols Daughter Beauty Products. In this interview Lisa shares three key points essential to starting up any new venture tenacity, confidence and balance.\n\nLisa began her beauty products empire by opening up her home for people to shop in her living room. After a 6 year journey she took the step to expand into her first store. Today, Prices Carols Daughter Beauty Products are highly sought after all over the world and coveted by some of entertainments most popular celebrities.\n\n<b><i>Confidence is built in every failure.</i></b> As a small business owner, Price understood that failure will come. The confidence that it takes to own and operate a business comes with trial and error. As your business journey evolves your knowledge increases as does your passion for your craft. Becoming a better business leader is about building upon each loss; each failure; each setback to develop confidence in your craft and foster your success.\n\n<b><i>Balance is an art</i></b> Perfection is a verb! As a business owner, at any level, it is important to know that achieving perfection is a constant pursuit. <i>You have to be happy with being imperfecteverything will not get done</i>, says Price. Balance is an art, achieving it, as with any talent, takes practice; perspective and execution. Keep the main thing, the main thing!\n\n<b><i>TENACITYthe Golden Rule</i></b> Knowing that you are working towards a goal should invoke the intrinsic response of the moth drawn to the flame. As an entrepreneur, your desire to succeed has to be greater than your fear of failure. Tenacity is the golden rule of reaching the finish line no matter if its firstlastor after 6 years of selling perfume in your living room.\n\n\n\n', 'br', 1368734580, '', 'none', 'Feel the Fear and Do It Anyway!', 'none', 'Feel the Fear and Do It Anyway!', 'none', 'Feel the Fear, Do It Anyway', 'none', 'Feel the Fear and Do It Anyway!', 'none', '{filedir_1}LISA-PRICE-SCREEN-SAVER.jpg', 'none', 'Feel the Fear and Do It Anyway!', 'none', 'Publisher Business Accelerator', 'none', '', 'none', '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', NULL, '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', 'Feel the Fear and Do It Anyway!', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', 0, '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', 0, 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'xhtml', '', 'xhtml', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none', '', 'none'),
